                     <br/>NDC 43093-104-01
       
 
  <br/>
                     <br/>Rx only
       
 
  <br/>
                     <br/>FusePaq™   Oral Suspension Kit
       
 
  <br/>
                     <br/>DICOPANOL™
       
 
  <br/>
                     <br/>(diphenhydramine hydrochloride 5 mg/mL, in oral suspension kit)
       
 
  <br/>
                     <br/>Description:
       
 
  <br/>This kit contains active and inactive bulk materials to prepare 150 mL of a  diphenhydramine hydrochloride oral suspension containing 5 mg/mL diphenhydramine hydrochloride. This kit may only be used for the extemporaneous combining of these ingredients by an appropriate licensed medical professional in response to a physician's prescription to create a medication tailored to the specialized needs of an individual patient. 
       
 
  <br/>Active Ingredient:
       
 
  <br/>
                  </paragraph>
                  <list listType="unordered">
                     <item>0.75 g diphenhydramine hydrochloride, USP</item>
                  </list>
                  <paragraph>Inactive Ingredients:
       
 
  <br/>
                  </paragraph>
                  <list listType="unordered">
