                     <item>Press-in bottle adaptor for oral dispenser</item>
                     <item>Oral dispenser</item>
                     <item>Instructions</item>
                  </list>
                  <paragraph>
                     <br/>Store kit at room temperature, 15-30 degrees C (59-86 degrees F)
       
 
